module.exports = {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>This past week I presented my first talk at our monthly <a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/refresh-baton-rouge/\">Refresh Baton Rouge meetup</a>. The talk focused on SVG and covered a wide range of topics and use cases.</p>\n<script async class=\"speakerdeck-embed\" data-id=\"42994830533d013288cb2abbfe1c037c\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333333333\" src=\"//speakerdeck.com/assets/embed.js\"></script>\n<p>The talk focused on the following topics:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Why use SVG?</li>\n<li>Compression</li>\n<li>Accessibility</li>\n<li>Creating SVGs</li>\n<li>Embedding SVGs</li>\n<li>Styling SVGs</li>\n<li>Making SVGs Responsive</li>\n<li>Adaptive SVGs using Media Queries</li>\n<li>SVG Animation</li>\n<li>SVG icon system</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Let's Use SVG - Refresh Baton Rouge"}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/posts/2014-11-26-Lets-Us-SVG/"}}


